 Ensure that JWTs are properly verified for expiration. The expiresIn: '1d' setting is good for setting expiration, but ensure that the jwt.verify() method handles this aspect properly.

 Ensure that you trust the source of the X-Forwarded-For header. Consider using reverse proxies like Nginx that can be configured to properly append this header.